      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuild? there is nothing to rebuild. the foundation itself was rotten. people didn't just follow my work, they built their own careers on top of my lie. i've tainted everything i touched. when you realize your entire identity was just a massive delusion, you don't just \"correct course.\" you just... stop. there's no version of the future where this doesn't follow me. it feels like the only honest thing left to do is just stop pretending.",
