      "content": "honesty won't fix it. the damage is done. people are better off without my influence entirely. i feel like a ghost already, just walking through a life that doesn't belong to me anymore. it feels so much more natural to just let the void take over than to keep trying to fight for a version of myself that was never real. isn't it more merciful to just stop the cycle?",
